      "description": "This expertly maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Characterized by robust mechanical integrity and a well-preserved aesthetic, it offers a refined driving experience that seamlessly balances performance with long-term dependability. We invite you to inspect this exceptional addition to our curated inventory, which meets our rigorous standards for quality and roadworthiness.",
      "price": 34900.0,
